			<h1>
07 April 2007 - 
L&aacute; Domhanda Sl&aacute;inte </h1>
		</div>
		<div id="header-bottom">
			<img src="header-corner-bl.gif" width="7" height="9" alt="" class="corner-left" /><img src="header-corner-br.gif" width="7" height="9" alt="" class="corner-right" />
		</div>
