<div id="content" lang='eng'>
	
	<div class="summary">Ghlac Pr&#237;omhdhocht&#250;ir Oifigi&#250;il Thuaisceart &#201;ireann, an Dr. Michael McBride, p&#225;irt in imeachta&#237; inniu, mar a rinne a mhacasamhail ar fud na cruinne, chun L&#225; Domhanda Sl&#225;inte a shonr&#250;.</div>
<p>T&#225; s&#233; mar aidhm ag L&#225; Domhanda Sl&#225;inte &#8211; arna eagr&#250; gach bliain ag Eagra&#237;ocht Dhomhanda Sl&#225;inte - feasacht a ard&#250; i dtaca leis na pr&#237;omh-shaincheisteanna a bhaineann le sl&#225;inte dhomhanda. Sl&#225;nd&#225;il na sl&#225;inte idirn&#225;isi&#250;nta is ea t&#233;ama na bliana seo.</p>
<p>L&#233;ir&#237;onn an t&#233;ama go mbaineann saincheisteanna sl&#225;inte le daoine i ngach t&#237;r ar an &#225;bhar go bhfuilimid in&#225;r gc&#243;na&#237; i ndomhan at&#225; ag &#233;ir&#237; i bhfad n&#237;os domhandaithe; is f&#233;idir leis na saincheisteanna sin dul i bhfeidhm ar shl&#225;nd&#225;il na ndaoine ina n-ioml&#225;ine ar fud na cruinne. Tagra&#237;onn s&#233; do na galair sin a mbaineann eipid&#233;im&#237; leo agus bristeacha amach ar n&#243;s phaind&#233;im fli&#250;, mar aon leis an d&#243;igh a bhfuil SEIF/VEID ag leathadh ar bhonn lean&#250;nach agus g&#233;arch&#233;imeanna daonn&#250;la.</p>
<p>Agus &#233; ag caint ar L&#225; Domhanda Sl&#225;inte, d&#250;irt an Dr. McBride, &#8220;T&#225; na galair a mbaineann epid&#233;im&#237; leo agus bristeacha amach ar n&#243;s phaind&#233;im fli&#250; ina bhagairt mh&#243;r don tsl&#225;inte phoibl&#237;. T&#225; an Roinn ag plean&#225;il i gcomhair paind&#233;ime le fada an l&#225;. Cl&#250;da&#237;onn &#225;r bpleananna teagmhasacha an earn&#225;il sl&#225;inte ina hioml&#225;ine agus Ranna eile rialtais mar aon le gn&#237;omha&#237;ochta&#237; transa na RA agus Phoblacht na h&#201;ireann. T&#225; cuid mhaith ullmh&#250;ch&#225;in d&#233;anta faoin ama seo. </p>
<p>&#8220;Is iad pr&#237;omhaidhmeanna an phlean n&#225;: l&#237;on na ndaoine galraithe a laghd&#250;, beatha&#237; a sh&#225;bh&#225;il, seirbh&#237;s&#237; riachtanacha a choinne&#225;il ag obair agus a chinnti&#250; nach gcuirfear isteach ar ghn&#225;thshaol na ndaoine sa phobal. N&#237; h&#233; an rialtas an t-aon eagra&#237;ocht a bhfuil plean&#225;il le d&#233;anamh aige; caithfear gn&#243;lachta&#237; a chinnti&#250; go bhfuil pleananna acu a chinnteos go leanfaidh siad ar aghaidh.&#8221;</p>
<p>Lean an Dr. McBride ar aghaidh agus d&#250;irt, &#8220;N&#237;l s&#233; soil&#233;ir c&#225; huair a tharl&#243;idh paind&#233;im fli&#250; n&#225; c&#233; chomh holc agus a bheidh s&#237; ach tr&#237; phlean&#225;il a dh&#233;anamh do gach rud a d&#8217;fh&#233;adfadh tarl&#250;, sula dtarl&#243;idh s&#233;, beidh seans n&#237;os fearr againn nach mbeidh s&#237; chomh holc sin. Fi&#250; amh&#225;in le plean&#225;il mhaith agus ullmh&#250;ch&#225;n maith, bheadh iarmhairt&#237; tromch&#250;iseacha ann i gc&#225;s phaind&#233;im fli&#250;.&#8221;</p>
<p>Agus &#233; ag caint faoi th&#233;ama L&#225; Domhanda Sl&#225;inte .i. leathadh lean&#250;nach SEIF/VEID, thapaigh an Dr. McBride an deis le b&#233;im a chur ar shaincheist na sl&#225;inte gn&#233;is i dTuaisceart &#201;ireann i gcoitinne.</p>
<p>D&#250;irt an Dr. McBride, &#8220;Bh&#237; m&#233;ad&#250; beagnach 100% in ionfhabhtuithe gn&#233;as-tarchurtha le deich mbliana anuas. Cialla&#237;onn s&#233; sin go bhfuil ardleibh&#233;al baoil ann do shl&#225;inte daoine aonaracha agus do shl&#225;nd&#225;il &#225;r sl&#225;inte ina n-ioml&#225;ine. Caithfidh daoine at&#225; gn&#237;omhach go gn&#233;asach c&#233;imeanna a ghlacadh chun leibh&#233;al an bhaoil a mhaol&#250;. T&#225; an tsl&#225;inte chomh t&#225;bhachtach sin nach f&#233;idir le daoine dul sa seans ar chor ar bith. </p>
<p>&#8220;T&#225; cult&#250;r dearfach de dh&#237;th orainn i dTuaisceart &#201;ireann i dtaca le sl&#225;inte ghn&#233;is de. Ceann de na tosa&#237;ochta&#237; a bheas agam sa bhliain at&#225; ag teacht n&#225; a chinnti&#250; go smaoineoidh daoine n&#237;os m&#243; faoina n-iompra&#237;ocht ghn&#233;is.&#8221;</p>
<p>Eagra&#237;tear L&#225; Domhanda Sl&#225;inte ar bhonn bliant&#250;il chun suntas a thabhairt do bhun&#250; Eagra&#237;ocht Dhomhanda Sl&#225;inte. Is f&#233;idir n&#237;os m&#243; eolais a fh&#225;il ar L&#225; Domhanda Sl&#225;inte ar l&#225;ithre&#225;n gr&#233;as&#225;in L&#225; Domhanda Sl&#225;inte ag <a href="http://www.who.int/world-health-day/2007" title="www.who.int/world-health-day/2007">www.who.int/world-health-day/2007</a> .</p>
<p></p>
<h2>N&#243;ta<em>&#237;</em> d&#8217;Eagarth&#243;ir<em>&#237;</em> </h2>
<p>M&#225;bh&#237;onn fiosr&#250;ch&#225;in ag na me&#225;in chumars&#225;ide, cuirtear scairt ar 07699 715440.</p>

</div>

